data.description: Log home in the heart of Big Canoe built in 2004. It is a cozy and gorgeous North Georgia log cabin in the Big Canoe community. This chic and stylish home beautifully blends modern spaces and mountain charm. There are exposed beams and vaulted ceilings. Living rooms features floor to ceiling rock fireplace with a wood stove. Off the living room is an office/den.  The kitchen is fully equipped with newer appliances. Master suite on upper level with a morning porch. Master bath is charming. Hardwood floors throughout yet tile in bathrooms. Lower level has an additional living space with a family room. In addition it features two large bedrooms with a J&J bath, both rooms have access to a large deck. This home has been beautifully maintained. NEW ROOF AND FRESH PAINT!  All furnishings available on separate bill of sale AND at the right price everything could stay.
